OL,3,C60% of farmers 'at financial risk from
OL,4,Csupermarket buying behaviour' ` survey
OL,6,FSome six in 10 farmers say they
OL,7,Fconsider their farm to be at financial
OL,8,Frisk because of supermarket buying
OL,9,Fbehaviour, with the industry branding
OL,10,Fthe current regulatory scheme "unfit
OL,11,Ffor purpose".
OL,13,FSome 68% of farmers say making a
OL,14,Fliving through farming has "never been
OL,15,Fharder" while 69% believe the buying
OL,16,Frelationship between growers and
OL,17,Fretailers has deteriorated, according
OL,18,Fto a study led by vegetable box
OL,19,Fcompany Riverford.
