OL,6,FAlmost every farmer surveyed (99%)
OL,7,Fsaid they had faced at least one
OL,8,F'unfair' practice, including cancelled
OL,9,Forders, late payments, and
OL,10,Funfavourable, unfair or unprofitable
OL,11,Fpricing.
OL,13,FSupermarkets rejecting produce over
OL,14,Funreasonable demands, such as
OL,15,Frequiring a specific colour, size or
OL,16,Fshape, leading to waste or a lower
OL,17,Fprice that does not cover costs, are
OL,18,Falso cited, as is no notice from
OL,19,Fbuyers for changed terms.
