OL,6,FRiverford said this was piling
OL,7,Fpressure on stretched growers, with
OL,8,F82% of respondents saying unfair
OL,9,Fsupermarket practices were
OL,10,Fcontributing to stress and poor mental
OL,11,Fhealth among the farming community.
OL,13,FThe industry is calling for a single
OL,14,Ffood supply chain regulator to protect
OL,15,Fgrowers and ensure fair treatment by
OL,16,Fsupermarkets, and to address the
OL,17,F"power imbalance" between the two.
