OL,6,FHaydn Evans, a dairy farmer from
OL,7,FCarmarthen in Wales, said he
OL,8,Fsuccessfully pressured his milk buyer
OL,9,Fto pass on a 1p per litre price rise
OL,10,Ffrom supermarkets, only to find out
OL,11,Fthat the buyer was then de-listed just
OL,12,Fthree months later.
OL,14,FHe said: "Supermarkets know how much
OL,15,Fthey're taking and how vulnerable
OL,16,Ffarmers are ` they exploit the power
OL,17,Fimbalance.
OL,19,F"They know that you are always
OL,20,Fnegotiating with two hands tied behind
OL,21,Fyour back."
