OL,6,FRiverford founder Guy Singh Watson
OL,7,Fsaid: "For three years our
OL,8,F_GetFairAboutFarming campaign has been
OL,9,Fcalling for a regulator with real
OL,10,Fteeth, one that can stand up to
OL,11,Fsupermarkets and help address the huge
OL,12,Fimbalance of power in our supply
OL,13,Fchains.
OL,15,F"Over 113,000 people have backed that
OL,16,Fcall, and even Parliament has debated
OL,17,Fit, yet farmers are still being failed
OL,18,Fby a system that's meant to protect
OL,19,Fthem.
