OL,4,Csupermarket buying behaviour' ` survey
OL,6,F"The Groceries Code Adjudicator's own
OL,7,Fresearch suggests things are improving
OL,8,Fand that may be the case for the large
OL,9,Fcompanies with supermarket contracts,
OL,10,Fbut our findings show the opposite is
OL,11,Ftrue for the small and medium-sized
OL,12,Ffamily farms that produce most of our
OL,13,Ffood.
OL,15,F"The problem is worse than ever, with
OL,16,F69% of farmers saying relations with
OL,17,Fsupermarkets have deteriorated over
OL,18,Fthe last two years.
