OL,3,C60% of farmers 'at financial risk from
OL,4,Csupermarket buying behaviour' ` survey
OL,6,F"Farming shouldn't feel like survival.
OL,7,FIt should be a livelihood to be proud
OL,8,Fof: producing good food, caring for
OL,9,Fthe land and looking after the people
OL,10,Fwho work it.
OL,12,F"How can farmers do the right thing
OL,13,Ffor their soil, their animals and the
OL,14,Fplanet if they're squeezed for every
OL,15,Fpenny and lack the funds and security
OL,16,Fto invest in farming well for the long
OL,17,Fterm? And how can shoppers make good
OL,18,Fchoices when they're being misled by
OL,19,Fsupermarket farmwashing?"
