OL,7,Fcampaign officer at the food and
OL,8,Ffarming alliance Sustain, said: "The
OL,9,Flatest research from Riverford clearly
OL,10,Fshows that farmers continue to be
OL,11,Fnegatively affected by unfair trading
OL,12,Fpractices by supermarkets.
OL,14,F"Orders cancelled at short notice and
