OL,6,F"It is deeply concerning that three-
OL,7,Fquarters of farmers say that
OL,8,Fretailers' behaviour is driving farms
OL,9,Ftowards more intensive,
OL,10,Fenvironmentally damaging practices.
OL,12,F"Without taking more ambitious action
